channel.title: Looking for an experienced partner #No Noobs Allowed
channel.description:
Hello and welcome, i'm looking for a partner or two who is also in my position. I want to start a server but not just any server, i want ours to be outstanding and for this reason i will only be looking for 1/2 coders experienced in 503+ (Not decided on which revision yet) if you think you can fill the spot then hit me up on Skype.
Skype: BengsPB

item.title: Looking for an experienced partner #No Noobs Allowed
item.dc:creator: @runescape_sucks runescape sucks
item.description:
@runescape_sucks wrote:

Sorry, I couldn’t hear the sarcasm in your voice, it’s kinda hard to tell over the internet.

In all seriousness, who are you? You have nothing to offer, apparently, and to be honest, you seem a bit too immature to be running a server.

And think about it like this, why would someone want to help you develop your server if they could just do it themselves, and do it how they want it?
